<%- include("partials/header", title) -%>
    <!--Carousel-->
    <section>
        <div class="position-absolute w-5 z-index-2 top-25 end-0 text-end m-5 blur d-none d-sm-block">
            <p id="carousel-title" class="h1 text-gold">Join Today</p>
            <p id="carousel-sub" class="sub text-white">We want you</p>
        </div>

        <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-indicators">
                <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleControls" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active"
                    aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
                <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleControls" data-bs-slide-to="1"
                    aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
                <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleControls" data-bs-slide-to="2"
                    aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="/static/img/1.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/static/img/2.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/static/img/3.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleControls" data-bs-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
            </button>
            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleControls" data-bs-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
            </button>
        </div>


    </section>

    <!--Main content-->
    <section class="border-gold border-top">

        <div class="container">
            <div class="mt-5 mb-5">
                <h2>About us</h2>
                <p>We're a UK based Arma 3 milsim group who started out as a bunch of friends running some hastily made halo themed zeus missions.
                    Since then we've amassed a bigger group of players and host sessions fairly regularly.
                    <br><br>
                    We don't base our unit around any one particular real life unit or military force, instead we run story based campaigns themed around different military forces or factions.
                </p>
            </div>
    
            <div class="row gx-5 w-100 mb-5">
                <div class="col-12 col-md">
                    <p class="h5 text-white">Structured Campaigns</p>
                    <p>We create our own scenarios of around 3-5 intertwined missions per campaign, allowing you to get immersed in the player faction and understand the conflicts at hand.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <p class="h5 text-white">Semi-Serious Roleplay</p>
                    <p>Long gone are the days of "Yes, Sir - No, Sir!" <br> We take a more laid back approach to the roleplay inside of missions, focusing on the enjoyment factor over anything else.
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row gx-5 w-100">
                <div class="col-12 col-md">
                    <p class="h5 text-white">Training Progression</p>
                    <p>Using our member dashboard we have a selection of training courses available, allowing for both the experts of Arma and the fresh beginners to enjoy our milsim events.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <p class="h5 text-white">More than a community!</p>
                    <p>As well as Arma Milsim, we also play a plethora of other games together, and regularly host events and gaming sessions on our main Discord server.</p>

                </div>
            </div>

            
            
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-5">
        <div class="container mb-5">
            <h2>Kingdom of Reign</h2>
            <div class="row gx-5 w-100 mt-5 d-inline d-md-flex">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-5 mb-md-0">
                    <div class="card bg-subduedgrey">
                        <div class="card-header d-block d-lg-flex">
                            <div class="col title-holder mt-2">
                                Reign Milsim
                                <p>
                                <em>"Campaign Name"</em>
                                </p>    
                            </div>
                            <div id="server-status" class="col rounded-5 milsim-inactive text-center pt-2 pb-2">
                                <p class="fw-bolder">Duty Status here</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-body d-none d-lg-flex bg-brightgrey">
                            <div class="col">
                                Members in session:
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Member</li>
                                    <li>Member</li>
                                    <li>Member</li>
                                    <li>Member</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col bg-grey rounded-1 bg-dark px-0 text-center">
                                    <img class="rounded-1" src="/static/img/1.png" style="width:100%;height:50%">

                                Campaign Name
                                <p class="text-start m-1">
                                    aodisdou shdosaudbn soubdaisudbs idsbapdb
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <iframe class="w-100"
                    src="https://discord.com/widget?id=311612862554439692&theme=dark"
                        allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" 
                        sandbox="allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts"></iframe>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <%- include("partials/footer") -%>